<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Therapy Session Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4A90E2;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .session-card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: white;
    }
    .session-info {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .session-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4A90E2;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Upcoming Therapy Session</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>This is a friendly reminder about your upcoming therapy session:</p>
      
      <div class="session-card">
        <h3 class="session-info">{{sessionTitle}}</h3>
        <p class="session-info"><strong>Date:</strong> {{sessionDate}}</p>
        <p class="session-info"><strong>Time:</strong> {{sessionTime}} ({{sessionTimezone}})</p>
        <p class="session-info"><strong>Therapist:</strong> {{therapistName}}</p>
        <p class="session-info"><strong>Session Type:</strong> {{sessionType}}</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;">
          <a href="{{sessionJoinUrl}}" class="session-button">Join Session</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p>Please ensure you're in a quiet, private space with a stable internet connection for your session.</p>
      
      <p>Need to reschedule? Please give at least 24 hours notice by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Using the reschedule feature in your MindLyf dashboard</li>
        <li>Contacting your therapist directly</li>
        <li>Emailing our support team at support@mindlyf.com</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>We look forward to supporting your mental health journey.</p>
      <p>Warm regards,<br>The MindLyf Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{year}} MindLyf. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a> | 
        <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="{{termsUrl}}">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 